high_descs: turn to the left to face the sink
open the cabinet door on the right underneath the sink, remove the bar of soap and close the door
turn around and move forward to the bath tub
put the bar of soap in to the bath tub
move slightly to the left still facing the bath tub
pick up the bar of soap that  is in the left back corner of the bath tub
move slightly to the right back to the center of the bath tub
put the second bar of soap in to the bath tub to the right of the first bar
anns.task_desc: put two bars of soap in to the bath tub

high_descs: Face the sink on your left.
Open the cabinet under the sink, take the soap out of the cabinet and close the cabinet.
Turn around and face the tub in front of you.
Place the soap in the tub in front of you.
Turn left and face the tub on your right.
Take the other soap from the tub in front of you.
Turn right and face the tub on your left.
Place the soap in the tub in front of you.
Turn to the left and face the sink.
Open the bottom right cabinet and pick up the soap. Shut the door.
Hold the soap and turn around and face the bath tub.
Place the soap inside the bath tub.
Take a step to the left of the bath tub.
Pick up the bar of soap from the edge.
Hold the soap and take a step to the right.
Place the soap inside the bath tub, to the right of the other soap.
anns.task_desc: Move two bars of soap to the bath tub.
